data.description: Welcome to 40 Christopher Way, a stunning largest lot single-family home in Park Ridge community located  in the heart of Stafford, VA. This exquisite property offers 4 bedrooms, optional 5th bedroom in the basement,3.5 bathrooms, and a huge back yard, providing ample space for comfortable living and entertaining.  As you step inside, you'll be greeted by an open concept filling the home with natural light. The interior features a perfect blend of carpet, ceramic, hardwood, and tile floors, along with skylights and recessed lighting, creating a warm and inviting ambiance throughout.    The spacious kitchen is a chef's delight, boasting stainless steel appliances, granite countertops, an island, and an open layout ideal for both casual dining and formal gatherings. The main level also includes a formal dining room, a home office, an inviting foyer, and a convenient powder room.  The primary ensuite bathroom offers a luxurious retreat with ceramic finishes, a separate shower, and a soaking tub, complemented by a walk-in closet for added convenience.  Outside, the property features a private yard, perfect for enjoying outdoor activities and relaxation. Additional amenities include a full basement, attached garage, security system, video intercom, and central air conditioning. Don't miss the opportunity to make this remarkable property your new home. Schedule a showing today and experience the unparalleled luxury and comfort of 40 Christopher Way.
